那看来我得亲自去找了

355
00:22:17,120 --> 00:22:19,399
Well, you found your way to the drinks cabinet all right.
嗯 你都已经找到酒柜了

356
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:21,879
I can't imagine the pantry will long prove terra incognita.
食品柜不会那么难找吧

357
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:24,400
Oh, yes, always the Latin!
噢 得了 又拽拉丁语

358
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:28,840
Must come in very handy consorting with the criminal classes.
跟犯罪分子打交道定能派上用场

359
00:22:30,040 --> 00:22:32,039
I expect this is one of yours, is it?
我猜这也是你们的案子吧

360
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:35,399
Taxi drivers murdered in nudist camps.
出租车司机在天体营被谋杀

361
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:37,879
