让他显得渺小

376
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:18,319
I can't imagine your father and this dead man have a thing in common.
我想不到你父亲和这个死者有任何共同点

377
00:23:18,320 --> 00:23:20,799
Well, there's the horses. Our dead man liked to gamble.
嗯 赌马 我们的死者也喜欢赌马

378
00:23:20,800 --> 00:23:22,559
