这没什么问题

379
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:24,479
A lot of men like a flutter.
很多男人觉得小赌怡情

380
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:28,079
Oh, and he left his wife and child for another woman that he'd, erm...
噢 他还抛妻弃子 去找别的女人 呃

381
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:29,999
