Hey!
嘿

419
00:25:43,560 --> 00:25:45,839
You're too young to be in possession of a firearm.
你太小了 不能持枪

420
00:25:45,840 --> 00:25:48,399
And it's not for you to find out who killed your father.
你也不该来找杀害你父亲的凶手

421
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,999
No matter how much you might want to.
不管你多想亲自出马

422
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:52,279
I'm staking out the crime scene, in case he comes back.
我要盯着犯罪现场 以防他回来

423
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:54,119
No, you're going home. And I'm taking you.
不 你回家去 我送你

424
00:25:54,120 --> 00:25:56,159
I know you want to help, but this isn't the way.
我知道你想帮忙 但这样不是办法

425
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,600
Jump in the car.
上车

426
00:26:58,040 --> 00:27:00,679
She won't be a minute, if you want to come up.
她马上就好 你要上来吗

427
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:02,279
No, no, you're all right, I'll, er...
不用了 谢谢 我 呃

428
00:27:02,280 --> 00:27:03,640
I'll wait here.
我就在这等

429
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:15,599
Is it, erm...?
漂亮吗

430
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:17,439
Yeah.
嗯

431
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,600
Oh, yeah.
噢 当然

432
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:23,559
-I'd forgot to say about gloves.  -I asked someone who'd been to one.
-我忘了说要戴手套了  -我问了去过的人

433
00:27:23,560 --> 00:27:26,600
-I didn't want to let the side down.  -You couldn't.
-我不想让大家失望  -不会的

434
00:27:34,840 --> 00:27:36,000
Should we...?
要出发吗

435
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,360
Yeah, yeah, of course.
啊 对 走吧

436
00:27:39,840 --> 00:27:41,280
I got you these.
我给你带了花

437
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:43,520
Thank you.
谢谢

438
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:46,240
Shall we...?
走吧

439
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:55,840
-Let me get you the door.  -Thanks.
-我来为你开门  -多谢

440
00:28:01,560 --> 00:28:03,480
Mind your dress.
当心裙子

441
00:28:06,280 --> 00:28:08,160
Don't you look a picture.
你真是美如画

442
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:22,279
-Shall we, squire?  -Let's.
-走吗 先生  -走吧

443
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:42,439
I thought, if I got a better report, he might come back.
我以为 要是我成绩变好 他就会回来

444
00:28:42,440 --> 00:28:43,839
How do you mean?
什么意思

445
00:28:43,840 --> 00:28:45,239
From school.
学校

446
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:47,839
I got a bad report and he was cross about it.
寄来了我的成绩单 很差 他很生气

447
00:28:47,840 --> 00:28:49,960
Then he went and lived with his new family.
然后他就走了 去和他的新家人一起住

448
00:28:51,760 --> 00:28:53,159
But...
但

449
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,960
Well, that was just a coincidence.
那只是个巧合

450
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:57,439
That wasn't your fault.
不是你的错

451
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:59,399
Your mum and dad getting divorced
你爸妈离婚

452
00:28:59,400 --> 00:29:02,399
had nothing to do with anything that you said or did,
和你的所作所为或不作不为

453
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:05,000
or didn't do or say. Do you understand?
没有任何关系 明白吗

454
00:29:06,520 --> 00:29:08,560
He was a good dad.
他是个好爸爸

455
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:12,079
Yeah, I'm sure. I'm sure.
嗯 确实 确实

456
00:29:12,080 --> 00:29:13,799
He'd let me help at the garage sometimes
他开出租车的时候

457
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:16,479
-when he was working on the cab.  -Yeah?
-有时会让我去修车厂帮忙  -是吗

458
00:29:16,480 --> 00:29:18,480
Did you enjoy that?
你喜欢吗

459
00:29:22,040 --> 00:29:24,319
Can I have my gun back?
我能拿回我的枪吗

460
00:29:24,320 --> 00:29:25,559
No.
不行

461
00:29:25,560 --> 00:29:27,159
Er, you can't. It's...
呃 不行 这是

462
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,919
It's illegal, I'm afraid.
这是违法的

463
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:31,759
You're just as likely to hurt yourself with it as someone else.
你和其他人一样 很可能伤到自己

464
00:29:31,760 --> 00:29:34,600
So, I'll keep hold of it until you're old enough, all right?
所以 我替你代为保管 直到你长大 好吗

465
00:29:36,360 --> 00:29:38,879
Now, go on. Go in and give your mum a hug.
好了 去吧 进去给你妈妈一个拥抱

466
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:40,120
Tell her you love her.
告诉她你爱她

467
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:30,320
Goodnight.
再见

468
00:30:33,040 --> 00:30:34,279
Can I see?
我能看看吗

469
00:30:34,280 --> 00:30:36,000
Oh, certainly.
当然可以

470
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:41,759
It's amazing.
太美了

471
00:30:41,760 --> 00:30:43,519
You're very welcome to it.
你可以拿走它

472
00:30:43,520 --> 00:30:45,759
You mean it, I could keep it?
你是说 我能留下它吗

473
00:30:45,760 --> 00:30:47,400
By all means, if you'd like it.
要是你喜欢 请务必收下

474
00:30:48,920 --> 00:30:50,439
Could you sign it?
你能签个名吗

475
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:51,840
Oh, now...
行

476
00:30:58,440 --> 00:31:00,119
-How's that?  -R Bright.
-怎么样  -R Bright

477
00:31:00,120 --> 00:31:01,479
What does the R stand for?
R是什么的缩写

478
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:02,919
Reginald.
Reginald

479
00:31:02,920 --> 00:31:04,559
I'm Lynn.
我是Lynn

480
00:31:04,560 --> 00:31:07,120
-Lynn Parry.  -Miss Parry, how do you do?
-Lynn Parry  -Parry小姐 你好啊

481
00:31:08,080 --> 00:31:09,480
Lynn.
叫Lynn就好

482
