别晚上好了 你想干嘛

498
00:32:56,760 --> 00:32:59,400
-I'm looking for Miss Thursday.  -Well, she's out.
-我找Thursday小姐  -她出门了

499
00:33:00,600 --> 00:33:01,839
Out?
出门

500
00:33:01,840 --> 00:33:05,160
Some bloke in an evening suit and a private car.
跟一个穿晚礼服 坐私家车的家伙

501
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:07,759
Oh...
噢

502
00:33:07,760 --> 00:33:09,800
-Was there a message?  -No.
-要留言吗  -不用

503
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:12,240
No, no message.
不用留言

504
00:33:17,280 --> 00:33:21,479
# Earth angel, Earth angel
# 凡间天使 凡间天使

505
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:24,839
# Will you be mine?
# 你会属于我吗

506
00:33:24,840 --> 00:33:27,799
# My darling, dear
# 我亲爱的 亲爱的

507
00:33:27,800 --> 00:33:31,519
# Love you all the time...
# 爱你到永远

508
00:33:31,520 --> 00:33:34,079
-Here we go...  -Thank you.
-给  -谢谢

509
00:33:34,080 --> 00:33:37,319
-All right?  -So far, so good.
-还好吗  -目前还行

510
00:33:37,320 --> 00:33:39,559
I didn't say anything that was...? Mm.
我是不是说错话了

511
00:33:39,560 --> 00:33:41,640
No. No, not at all. You were brilliant.
不 完全没有 你棒极了

512
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:46,480
So...
所以

513
00:33:47,520 --> 00:33:49,080
..what's this all about, then, Jim?
Jim 这活动是干嘛的

514
00:33:50,320 --> 00:33:53,400
Well, it's kind of expected, isn't it, in my line?
呃 这不是像我们这样的人应该做的嘛

515
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:57,719
Not many of us went to the right kind of school, so...
我们之中很多人都没去过正经学校

516
00:33:57,720 --> 00:34:00,159
-..this is the next best thing.  -Old boy network.
-但这样也不错  -校友关系网嘛

517
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:01,719
If you like.
这么说也可以

518
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:04,479
There's no harm in it. The way people go on,
这事也没害处 这里人做事的方式

519
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:07,320
you'd think it's all black magic and sacrificing virgins.
会觉得是在施展什么黑魔法 还要献祭处女

520
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:10,599
